Package: polcaExtra
Type: Package
Title: Extended Interface for Latent Class Analysis Models
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Piotr Tymoszuk <piotr.s.tymoszuk@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides an extended diagnostic and graphical S3 
    interface for latenc class models (LCA) fited with the package poLCA. 
    Handy methods for retrieval of the model components and predictions are
    implemented as well.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
